The STARWEST Virtual+ Experience    
    
  
  
    In light of recent events, TechWell has morphed the popular STARWEST conference into a fully virtual experience this year! From the comfort of your own digital device, you will have access to all of the same great content and experts you have come to expect from a STAR conference. STARWEST Virtual+ will be streaming over 75+ talks—including keynotes, tutorials, and sessions  all in an engaging and interactive premium virtual atmosphere. Plus, with 3 packages to choose from and a variety of exciting add-on options (such as a live virtual training class), you can select the conference package that fits your needs and your budget!
